<h1>Company Assets</h1>
<p>
	Acting as the main touchpoint for building our brand recognition,
	all assets should be used in a logical sense without any transformations or color adjustments.
</p>
<p>
	Asset names for company assets are defined by the pattern <code><strong>wds-company-logo-ASSET_NAME</strong></code>,
	e.g. <code>wds-company-logo-fandom</code>.
</p>
{{#link-to 'overview.svg-assets'}}How to use SVG assets{{/link-to}}

<section>
	<h2 id="fandom-logo">Fandom logo</h2>
	<p>This is base Fandom logo.</p>

	<div class="assets-wrapper assets-wrapper__align-items-left">
		{{asset-box group='company-logo' name='fandom' class='is-identity is-bordered is-single-in-line' width=300 height=120}}
	</div>

	{{#component-demo name='assets-fandom' codeOnly=true}}
		{{svg 'wds-company-logo-fandom'}}
	{{/component-demo}}
</section>

